divs: Sighting DetailsI was out at the lake here in winslow with a female friend and i lit up a cigarette and look up and saw this triangle shaped very dark object that was low enough for me to see it but it had no lights and made a humming sound or something like it.This thing was huge to say the least and it blocked oput the stars and was very visable even though it was dark I watched this thing for about 30 mins. My female friend saw this object and freaked as i only stood in stunned silence.
Summary: dark object that was darker then the night sky
